training and is based on reciprocal interests. So, no country
should feel uneasy over the agreement."
</P>
<P>
Mubarak expressed pleasure over the level of the bilateral
relations between Turkey and Israel, adding: "We have reviewed
the stage of the Middle East peace process. We have agreed that
the concerned sides should abide by their commitments coming from
international agreements."
</P>
<P>
An agreement on good neighborhood, friendship and cooperation
between Turkey and Egypt will be signed when Demirel visits Egypt
in the future, Mubarak added. 
