<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 11 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 12 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
July 12, issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at 17:00
today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 20 degrees c., max. 26 degrees c., overcast to
thunder showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. 20 degrees c., max. 28 degrees c., thunder
showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. 19 degrees c., max. 29 degrees c., drizzle to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. 21 degrees c., max. 36 degrees c., clear to cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chengdu: min. 25 degrees c., max. 33 degrees c., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Kunming: min. 16 degrees c., max. 25 degrees c., drizzle to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai: min. 22 degrees c., max. 30 degrees c., heavy rain to
thunder showers, moderate to fresh breeze.
</P>
<P>
Wuhan: min. 23 degrees c., max. 31 degrees c., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hangzhou: min. 23 degrees c., max. 28 degrees c., heavy rain to
moderate rain, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Taipei: min. 27 degrees c., max. 35 degrees c., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 26 degrees c, max. 33 degrees c., thunder
showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 27 degrees c., max. 33 degrees c., drizzle,
gentle to moderate breeze. 
