(WTO), Li said that the acceptance of China into the WTO will
contribute to the improvement of an international, multi-lateral
trade system, which will help strengthen the WTO's function and
unilateral needs.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, he added, China is willing to continue dialogues
with the concerned parties to resolve this issue, based on a
balance between rights and obligations.
</P>
<P>
Li also appreciated Japanese Prime Minister Ryutaro Hashimoto
and the Japanese Government for the positive attitude they have
adopted on this issue.
</P>
<P>
