were kidnaping five children at Ipregaz District in Batman late
Wednesday night, when the security forces following the PKK
rebels clashed with them.
</P>
<P>
The security forces rescued the five children but the three
soldiers suffered bullet wounds in the clash, it said.
</P>
<P>
