awards in national and regional levels to those industries
contributing to creating more jobs.
</P>
<P>
According to the budget report, special incentives like income
tax exemption will be provided to technical vocational institutes
and skill training centers with a view to encouraging the
development of skilled manpower in the country.
</P>
<P>
A high-level central coordination committee and similar
district level committees will be constituted in the 1996-97
fiscal year to formulate, implement and monitor the employment-
oriented policy and maintain inter-agency coordination.  
