been discovered. Furong cave in Wulong, regarded as the most
beautiful, has had 350,000 visitors since it opened to
sight-seeing in 1994.
</P>
<P>
In the area's mountains there are many grasslands dotted with
forests, wild flowers, and herds of cattle and sheep. For
residents of southern China, the grasslands are quite a rare sight.
</P>
