foreign trade decreased.
</P>
<P>
Central American countries will be seeking Chilean investment
during the meeting, the sources said.
</P>
<P>
The countries are also expected to start talks on a free trade
agreement.
</P>
<P>
Some 200 Central American and Chile businessmen will meet to
discuss possible businesses chances.
</P>
<P>
Politicians from these countries will debate on "democratic
governance" and other important regional political issues during
the meeting, the sources added. 
