<HEADLINE> Media Becoming Investment Advisors for Shanghai's Citizens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, July 11 (Xinhua) -- The press in China's leading
financial center and biggest industrial city have turned out to be
sound investment advisors for the citizens of Shanghai.
</P>
<P>
With the increase in individual incomes, the city's residents
have begun to take an interest in 'investing', something that has
become a household word in the city.
</P>
<P>
Statistics showed that the stock market attracted some 7
million Shanghai citizens by the end of last year, and Shanghai
Securities, China's first securities newspaper, is one of the most
widely read in the city.
</P>
<P>
Even local newspapers, such as The Liberation Daily and Xinmin
Evening News are carrying daily stock quotations, while local
television stations feature financial and economic news, with
stock indexes and prices, on a daily basis.
</P>
<P>
Not to be outdone, radio stations give stock quotations every
other hour and invite financial experts to provide daily analyses
for traders after the closing of the market.
</P>
<P>
While all this is going on, collecting commemorative gold and
silver coins, works of art, and stamps, which can be an
investment, are also quite popular among Shanghai's citizens.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai's Business News runs a weekly column "Today's Stamp
Market", not only describing new stamps, but also offering
information on collecting art and other investment items, such as
a new variety of magnetic telephone card, or commemorative gold or
silver coins issued in limited amounts.
</P>
<P>
Ma Dongcheng, an office employee, bought two paper fans with
inscriptions by famous calligraphers for several thousand yuan,
two years ago, at an auction fair. The price of these treasures
has gone up by about 70 percent. He had learned from newspapers
previously that works of art can be a kind of low-risk investment.
</P>
<P>
He said he believes that for people who do not have much money
and much time to play the stock exchange, collecting works of art
can be one of the best ways to make an investment. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
