<HEADLINE> Palestinians Protest against Israel's Delay of </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, July 10 (Xinhua) -- Dozens of Palestinians took to
the street today to protest against Israel's delay of redeployment
in the West Bank city of Hebron.
</P>
<P>
